"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-news-gayton-mckenzie-sa-team-cost-participation-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbNews ByEnkosi Selane Journalist 4 minute read 12 October 2024 08:28 pm Minister of Sport, Arts and Culture Gayton McKenzie.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Home\\u00bbNews\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 9}, {\"ngram\": \"ByEnkosi Selane Journalist\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 36}, {\"ngram\": \"4 minute\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 45}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 88, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"Arts\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"Culture\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Gallo Images Minister of Sport, Arts and Culture Gayton McKenzie revealed this week that government spent millions of rands for the country's top athletes to participate in the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"government\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 243}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"rands\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 267}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's top athletes\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This disclosure comes in response to a parliamentary question from Democratic Alliance (DA) MP, Joseph Job McGluwa.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republican_Alliance\", \"score\": 0.9999999962451511, \"rank\": 3.7547497483057885e-09, \"text\": \"Democratic Alliance\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republican_Alliance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Democratic_Republican_Alliance\"}, {\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Joseph\", \"score\": 0.9810621812055341, \"rank\": 0.019169013976186495, \"text\": \"Joseph\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Joseph\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Joseph\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This disclosure\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"a parliamentary question\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McKenzie reported that while exact costs per athlete were still being calculated, the budget for Team SA's support, preparation, and delivery to the Olympics tallied up to R27,892,000.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999964270501, \"rank\": 3.5371597887862976e-09, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"exact costs\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"the budget\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"delivery\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"R27,892,000\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said this amount only covered costs related to athletes and technical support for the 146 South African Olympic team.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"South African Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this amount\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"technical support\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The South African Sports Confederation and Olympic Committee in their response has indicated that invoices are still being processed for the Olympic Games and are therefore unable to quantify the cost per athlete at the time of this response,\\\" said McKenzie.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The South African Sports Confederation\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Committee\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"their response\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"invoices\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"this response\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to athlete-related expenses, it was revealed that the government allocated R1,805,335.74 for official travel to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete-related expenses\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"official travel\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This budget covered eight officials, including the minister himself, who attended the Games.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This budget\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"eight officials\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"the minister\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No other officials from the Department of Sport, Arts, and Culture (DSAC) traveled to the Olympics,\\\" McKenzie emphasised.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No other officials\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"the Department\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"Arts\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"Culture\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"DSAC\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The total expenditure, combining athlete support and official travel, amounts to nearly R30 million.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The total expenditure\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete support\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"official travel\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:Sascoc commits to providing more support for Olympic athletes Despite this considerable investment, South Africa's performance at the Paris Olympics was modest compared to some nations with similar-sized delegations.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999056399, \"rank\": 8.9123553373052e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sascoc\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"more support\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"this considerable investment\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"some nations\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"similar-sized delegations\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1719}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 146 South African athletes secured six medals, including one gold.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 146 South African athletes\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"six medals\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"one gold\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In contrast, New Zealand, with 195 competitors, claimed 20 medals, ten of which were gold.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contrast\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"New Zealand\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"195 competitors\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"20 medals\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In light of these results, McKenzie announced an ambitious plan called \\\"Project 300\\\" aimed at doubling South Africa's Olympic team size for the 2028 Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 2001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999056399, \"rank\": 8.9123553373052e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"these results\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"an ambitious plan\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Project\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2028 Los Angeles Games\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This initiative seeks to increase the number of athletes from the current 150 to 300, matching countries like New Zealand despite South Africa's much larger population.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999056399, \"rank\": 8.9123553373052e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This initiative\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"matching countries\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"New Zealand\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:'We will go big for LA': McKenzie promises athletes support for Games McKenzie previously outlined plans to fund this expansion through various sources.\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"READ:'We\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"McKenzie\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes support\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"Games McKenzie\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"this expansion\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"various sources\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He publicly committed to this goal, saying, \\\"I want to publicly say this today, as South Africa, we have the responsibility to take no less than 300 Olympians to the Games in 2028.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999056399, \"rank\": 8.9123553373052e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this goal\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"the responsibility\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"no less than 300 Olympians\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a promise, I am going to make it happen.\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a promise\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are going to take money from our department.\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"our department\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We spoke to Lotto, we spoke to SuperSport, we are speaking to different companies that are willing to put money into Project 300 where we are going to search for talent in South Africa,\\\" the minister explained.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2679, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottery\", \"score\": 0.9999999999336069, \"rank\": 6.379147490930304e-11, \"text\": \"Lotto\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lottery\"}, {\"begin\": 2839, \"end\": 2851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999056399, \"rank\": 8.9123553373052e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SuperSport\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"different companies\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"Project\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"the minister\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The minister said he saw this investment as necessary to uncover hidden talent across the country, particularly in rural and underprivileged areas.\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 3026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The minister\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"this investment\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2919}, {\"ngram\": \"hidden talent\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"rural and underprivileged areas\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the exact cost of this expanded program has not been disclosed, it is likely to significantly exceed the current expenditure on Olympic participation.\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the exact cost\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"this expanded program\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"the current expenditure\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3158}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic participation\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This raises questions about the return on investment for such a large-scale sporting initiative, especially in a country facing numerous socio-economic challenges.\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"the return\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"such a large-scale sporting initiative\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3281}, {\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 329